&lt;li&gt;Investigates gas-phase chemistry, surface adsorption and desorption kinetics, and transport phenomena that influence deposition behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defines and refines process windows that maximize film quality, uniformity, reproducibility, and throughput.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implements and interprets in-situ and ex-situ diagnostics to understand deposition chemistry and process behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
